1. *Tako* se već išlo, pa smo išli i mi. (So it was already going, so we went too.)
2. *Tako* ću da ti pomognem. (So I'll help you.)
3. *Tako* da je odlučeno. (So it's decided.)
4. *Tako* da se zna. (So that it is known.)
5. *Tako* da se ljudi divno druže. (So that people have a wonderful time together.)
6. *Tako* da se zna gde je šta. (So that it is known where is what.)
7. *Tako* da se sve zna. (So that everything is known.)
8. *Tako* da smo našli odgovor. (So that we found an answer.)